% B8 -- insertion sort.

/insertion { /n exch def /arr exch def 1 1 n 1 sub { /i exch def /key arr i get def /j i 1 sub def { j 0 lt { exit } if arr j get key gt { arr j 1 add arr j get put /j j 1 sub def } { exit } ifelse } loop arr j 1 add key put } for } def
/run { /a 100 array def 0 1 99 { /i exch def a i 99 i sub put } for a 100 insertion } def
1000 { run } repeat
quit
